How I'm stepping into 2023 😎🔥

I'm feeling soooooo grateful for this year because I once again have completely surprised myself

I'm grateful for the amazing friends I have, the amazing community I have built, and the opportunities I continue to attract. This year, I GREW. I took time to relax, meditate, attract, and now I only operate from a place of overflow. No more burning out, ladies; we're playing smarter now. 

2023 for me, is a year where I step into my whole self. 
What does that mean? No playing small, no limiting myself, no second guessing, no shining on one part but hiding the next. Y'all are about to get all of me in the best way possible. 

As human beings, we have many interests, loves, and passions, and we should embody and pursue all of them. So cheers to an amazing 2022. Thank you for the next-level opportunities, and I CANNOT WAIT to manifest the fuq out of 2023. 🥰🙌🏿

🎥 @rafareels 🔥

Moving your body is by far the best accessible luxury we have, and should be taking advantage of more. It's something about starting the week with movement that feels so good, freeing, and therapeutic. 

So, I’m dedicating these last months of 2023 to moving my body and being more consistent in the gym. Because I am pretty happy with my body, I tend to skip days from time to time, but babyyyy, how are you going to maintain it if you don’t move that body? Lol 

So get up, walk, run, do a home workout, just get moving.

 If you’re interested in the Toned & Curvy 30-day challenge, check out the link in my bio. It won’t be available for long, so grab it now! Happy Lifting! 🔥

🌟 How to Layer Your Nighttime Skincare Routine 🌙
Moisturization Nights 

✨ Cleanse: Start with Micellar Water or Cleansing Balm to remove makeup and sunscreen, ensuring a clean canvas for your routine.

✨ Gentle Cleansing: Use @iliabeauty Beauty Foaming Wash to thoroughly remove makeup and residue from the day.

✨ Prep and Hydrate: Spritz @peachandlily Glass Skin Veil Mist to prepare your skin for the next step - Hyaluronic Acid Serum, your secret weapon for intense hydration.

✨Vitamin C Serum: Apply to @skinceuticals brighten your skin and address hyperpigmentation.

✨Eye Care: Pamper the delicate eye area with @baborofficial Vitalizing Eye Cream, addressing concerns like puffiness and fine lines.

✨Moisturize: Using @elemis Pro-Collagen Hydrating Night Cream to increase oxygen levels and support skin regeneration.

✨Neck and Hands: Don’t forget to extend your skincare to your neck and hands for a complete glow.

✨Optional Finishing Touch: If extra hydration is needed, consider using a face oil or occlusive product to seal in moisture.

👑 POV: You’re stepping into the best era of your life. 

And want to know a secret? That can happen at any time. 

You can wait for the new year or you can start today ✨

Here are a few things you can implement starting today:

✨ A clear vision of where you want to be in life and matching that frequency.

✨ Surrounding yourself with nothing but happy, healthy, supportive people.

✨ Clearing out old clothes, old energy, and throwing away things that no longer serve who you want to be.

✨ Getting on a healthier diet/regimen; this means taking care of yourself inside and out.

✨ Only focus on what you want. I know this one may ruffle some feathers - but where attention goes, energy flows. By paying attention to what you want, you’re setting new patterns, new behaviors, and most importantly, a new embodiment. ❤️ 

#BecomingHer MasterClass coming soon 💫

Love and blessings to you and your journey 😎🥰😘

📸🔥 @rafareels

Why wait when you can start now? ✨

In reality, the holidays don’t demand us to eat and drink naughtily every day—we choose to do that, lol. And I know, I know, ‘cause I take part as well 🙈 but we don’t have to add on an extra 10 lbs. Here’s what I’m doing to have a healthy balance ✨

🔥 I’m still attending events but will work out the next day.

🔥 I’ll have the wine but will skip dessert.

🔥 I’ll enjoy myself at family functions and have Auntie’s pie but will meal prep at home.

Where there’s a will, there’s a way. Just remember, there is always a way, and your dream body counts on it 😎Happy Monday, my loves! 🍑🔥
